The Bleumi Pay SDK is a one-stop shop to help you integrate Algorand, Ethereum, ERC-20, xDai payments and/or payouts into your business or application. The SDK bundles [Bleumi Pay API](https://pay.bleumi.com/docs/#introduction) into one SDK to ease implementation and support.

bleumi-pay-sdk-python is a Python library that provides an interface between your Python application and [Bleumi Pay API](https://pay.bleumi.com/docs/#introduction). This tutorial covers the basics, including examples, needed to use the SDK.


